nodes.text: Prinspai was an  insectoid male soldier of the New Republic's 61st Mobile Infantry. During the Galactic Civil War, Prinspai was selected by Wyl Lark to fly an airspeeder in a makeshift squadron, due to a shortage of pilots following the attack on Cerberon by Colonel Soran Keize's 204th Imperial Fighter Wing.
Prinspai appeared in the 2020 novel Shadow Fall, written by Alexander Freed.
